{"id":308315,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-深圳维权人士杨林被以煽动颠覆国家政/","date":"2013-08-10T17:49:17Z","modified":"2017-02-21T20:57:10Z","title":"维权网 | 深圳维权人士杨林被以“煽动颠覆国家政权罪”逮捕（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙雨报道）本网获悉，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日在深圳被警方带走后失踪的杨林，已经被深圳市公安局福田分局以“涉嫌煽动颠覆国家政权罪”执行逮捕，逮捕日期是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日，目前杨林被关押在深圳市福田区看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>杨林于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>号晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>时在北京被北京警方抓走，于次日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>号上午释放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日杨林从北京前往广州，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日在与唐荆陵律师见面后，途中被深圳警方带走，随后与外界失去联系。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>本网信息员在居住在山东省聊城的杨林的哥哥通话中得知，杨林的父亲已亡故，家中老母亲患多种病症，仅靠每月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>元的遗属补助费为生。家人只收到杨林</span><span>的逮捕通知书，没有见到刑事拘留通知书，由于家中经济困窘，可能无力出钱为其聘请律师，为此家人非常焦急。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>杨林失踪后，百余名社会各界人士联名呼吁当局公开其失踪真相。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>杨林是山东省聊城地区临清市尚店人，现年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span><span>岁，他</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多岁到深圳打工谋生。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2006</span><span>年杨林因工伤事故依法上访维权，在上访过程中，他常常帮助底层民众伸张正义。并全身心地投入到维权和从事民主宪政活动中。他是《零八宪章》签署人之一、中国公民监政会会员、《开展政治对话，力争和平转型》的联署人之一、公民记者、人权捍卫者。在深圳工作中，杨林深深认识到独裁专制是腐败罪恶的根源，于是，他义无反顾地全身心投入到为弱势民众维权及民主宪政活动中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>多年来，杨林参加了数百次公民维权活动。他到现场见证钱云会事件，围观乌坎事件，为在北京露宿街头的维权者送棉衣和食物。为此，他遭受行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>次，判刑一年，劳教一年，非法拘禁和关黑监狱等迫害不计其数。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--CKeIcRxpxc/UgZYNeTbKmI/AAAAAAAAmpQ/ulsu7Je2EDI/s1600/%E6%9D%A8%E6%9E%97%E5%9D%90%E5%9C%A8%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%AE%B6%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3DSCI1254.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--CKeIcRxpxc/UgZYNeTbKmI/AAAAAAAAmpQ/ulsu7Je2EDI/s320/%E6%9D%A8%E6%9E%97%E5%9D%90%E5%9C%A8%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E5%AE%B6%E9%97%A8%E5%8F%A3DSCI1254.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Zx40cIRH2N4/UgZYOdh9R1I/AAAAAAAAmpY/gdUx9FrDvPo/s1600/%E5%A4%8D%E4%BB%B6+SAM_0086.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"261\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Zx40cIRH2N4/UgZYOdh9R1I/AAAAAAAAmpY/gdUx9FrDvPo/s320/%E5%A4%8D%E4%BB%B6+SAM_0086.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-dEJe7WhPNBQ/UgZYREfuVoI/AAAAAAAAmpg/-vA1OE26bE8/s1600/SAM_0086.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-dEJe7WhPNBQ/UgZYREfuVoI/AAAAAAAAmpg/-vA1OE26bE8/s320/SAM_0086.JPG\" width=\"227\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[15515,19196,29709]}